{"TopicId":200435,"ForumId":109,"TopicTitle":"Minimum Viable Population (MVP)","CreatedByName":"Lo.M","CreatedById":208979,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-02-17T20:04:04Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Lo.M","CreatedById":208979,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-02-17T20:04:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat is the minimum viable population (MVP) of kerbals?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Minimum_viable_population\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Minimum_viable_population\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is extremely important for any colonies.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Bej Kerman","CreatedById":182413,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-02-17T20:05:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027d imagine at least 2.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lo.M","CreatedById":208979,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-02-17T20:08:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223927862\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022200435\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221613592342\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022182413\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Bej Kerman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Bej Kerman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027d imagine at least 2.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOnly with that number would genetics problems probably happen.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerminator K-100","CreatedById":204357,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-02-17T20:20:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223927863\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022200435\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221613592508\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022208979\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Lo.M\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n8 minutes ago, Lo.M said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOnly with that number would genetics problems probably happen.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGiven that the Kerbals all seem to be clones, I would assume that they would be fine.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHowever given that in my headcanon they aren\u0027t clones, I\u00A0don\u0027t know? I think kerbals don\u0027t even have genes as their only traits are the courage, stupidity, occupation, and BadS-ery.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Bej Kerman","CreatedById":182413,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-02-18T13:38:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223927863\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022200435\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221613592508\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022208979\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Lo.M\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n17 hours ago, Lo.M said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223927862\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022200435\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221613592342\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022182413\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Bej Kerman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n17 hours ago, Bej Kerman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027d imagine at least 2.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOnly with that number would genetics problems probably happen.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI can\u0027t imagine the game will go into that much detail with when and how Kerbals can reproduce.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Aziz","CreatedById":150811,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-02-18T13:56:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223927863\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022200435\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221613592508\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022208979\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Lo.M\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n17 hours ago, Lo.M said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOnly with that number would genetics problems probably happen.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh no, all my Kerbals are going to have 100% stupidity, what will I do?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lo.M","CreatedById":208979,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-02-18T16:41:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223928242\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022200435\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221613655486\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022182413\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Bej Kerman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, Bej Kerman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI can\u0027t imagine the game will go into that much detail with when and how Kerbals can reproduce.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt doesn\u0027t have to be that realistic, but only 2 kerbals are enough to create a colony gives me a little discomfort when it comes to realism.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223928254\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022200435\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221613656595\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150811\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The Aziz\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, The Aziz said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh no, all my Kerbals are going to have 100% stupidity, what will I do?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n100% stupidity, they would be less efficient in their jobs, they would die sooner.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-02-18T16:47:07Z\u0022 title=\u002202/18/2021 04:47  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 18, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by Lo.M\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Aziz","CreatedById":150811,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-02-18T17:10:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo far the traits only affect their reactions, we don\u0027t know about anything else.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso, we know that many Kerbals will have to be brought in before they start reproducing (the mysterious Boom events related to discoveries IIRC) so I wouldn\u0027t worry about variety.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-02-18T17:11:18Z\u0022 title=\u002202/18/2021 05:11  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 18, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by The Aziz\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"shdwlrd","CreatedById":113880,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-02-18T17:14:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223928330\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022200435\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221613668235\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150811\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The Aziz\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, The Aziz said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso, we know that many Kerbals will have to be brought in before they start reproducing (the mysterious Boom events related to discoveries IIRC) so I wouldn\u0027t worry about variety.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt would be hard to explain when you drop a couple Kerbals off at a base and go back a few years later to a few more.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"jimmymcgoochie","CreatedById":199902,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-02-18T18:19:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u2019d say about 20\u00A0would be enough. Through the judicious application of Science! to determine *ahem* optimal genetic mixing\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:blush:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_embarrassed.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:blush:\u0022\u003E, a sufficiently genetically distinct population could be created to remain viable into the future. Another option is frozen embryos, which would be defrosted as needed to maintain genetic diversity for potentially centuries. Combine the two and you don\u2019t need a huge initial population,\u00A0just enough to simultaneously look after all those baby Kerbals and keep the colony running at the same time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}